{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3b8fd1ef7d","title":"周恩来接见毛里塔尼亚外宾后和一位翻译的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"917c728e30","index":0,"year":1967,"month":10,"day":17,"articleId":"3b8fd1ef7d"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"cea9ce86b7","name":"清查五·一六","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bf04068efe","type":"title","text":"周恩来接见毛里塔尼亚外宾后和一位翻译的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3b8fd1ef7d"},{"id":"cec53f69c2","type":"authors","text":"周恩来","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3b8fd1ef7d"},{"id":"9f0f3d6462","type":"paragraph","text":"一、“外联”（外交部联络站）核心组的检查我看过了，很不深刻，根本过不了关，我看了很生气。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3b8fd1ef7d"},{"id":"c1bccd80a3","type":"paragraph","text":"二、“外联”核心组与“6.16”有联系，直接或间接参预了“五·一六”的活动，过几天我要去揪人，我有材料。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3b8fd1ef7d"},{"id":"6b295c036c","type":"paragraph","text":"三、我现在不到外交部去，我要是去讲话，外交部联络站就垮台了。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3b8fd1ef7d"},{"id":"5675a907d0","type":"paragraph","text":"四、北外红旗大队打姚登山是错误的，但姚登山把红旗大队比作卡比卡米是严重的政治错误，对姚登山要一批二保。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3b8fd1ef7d"},{"id":"7b50b6d1d3","type":"paragraph","text":"五、外交部目前进行的四大是正常的，外交部乱的不够，还要大乱，但不许武斗。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3b8fd1ef7d"}],"page":{"id":"05b71ded0d","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3b8fd1ef7d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}